All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
Application
The Application class serves as the entry point for the Links game and is responsible for setting up the game environment.
Chain
The Chain class represents a doubly linked list of Link objects.
ChainTest
Tests for the Chain class.
Game
The Game class represents a game session where two players take turns selecting links from the ends of a chain.
GameTest
Tests for the Game class.
Link
The Link class represents a node in a linked list.
LinkTest
Tests for the Link class.
Player
The Player class represents a player in a game.
PlayerTest
Tests for the Player class.
